As we take all these measures, we must remain vigilant and continue with the public health interventions including physical distancing and restricting mass gatherings, as well as the hygiene measures that have had a real impact on infectious diseases.
My greatest wish for Kenya in 2021 is to see an articulated government Covid-19 vaccination strategy that covers the items enumerated here, and to get to the end of 2021 with a country that is largely Covid-free!
